<scopecontent>
<p>General Papers, 1876-1900, consists of the business and financial papers of the Wrights' general store. This series contains both receipts and invoices from a number of merchants and companies with whom Mary L. Wright did business, as well as advertisements of new merchandise. Also included in this series are insurance policies, as well as several art prints and miscellaneous notes. 
</p>
</scopecontent>

